      "body" : "That is correct.\n\nThe wallet file stores up to which block it has \"seen\" the chain. At\nstartup, an automatic rescan happens for exactly the missing part.\n\nA manual rescan should only be necessary when you use\nimportprivkey/importwallet with the rescan option set to false, if you are\nloading an extremely old wallet file (several years), or when you manually\ntweak the wallet file using external utilities.\n",
